Compact binaries provide a good system to study 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Astrophysics.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Test of GR.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Cosmology.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Extreme matter.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We will refer to the 
\begin_inset CommandInset href
